Primal Maelstrom is an Archdruid battlefield invocation.  It spends all
four currents to tear open a storm of root, fire, moonlight, and thunder
through the room.

The maelstrom damages enemies and briefly disrupts their concentration.
It is expensive, but it is pure spellcraft: no weapon, no form, no melee
setup.
